"""
AI Trading Bot — Main Entry Point (Hardened for VPS 24/7)

Full pipeline: DATA → HEALTH CHECK → INDICATORS → VOLUME → RULE → AI → NEWS → RISK → EXECUTION

Safety features:
- MT5 Health Monitor (connection check every cycle)
- Global Watchdog (heartbeat, auto-recovery)
- Safe Execution Gate (pre-trade validation)
- Degraded mode fallback (AI/News failure never crashes)
- Crash-proof outer loop (never stops unless killed)
"""

